videos.description: Dayton's Iba Watson slams on brakes and spins, then drains the midrange jumper.
videos.headline: Watson's spin move fools defender

videos.description: Saint Louis' Jordan Goodwin fights for an offensive rebound, then scores on a nice reverse lay-in.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Goodwin snags offensive board, finishes with reverse layup) 2020/01/17

videos.description: After trailing since the 17:54 mark in the first half, Trey Landers' three-pointer gives Dayton the lead with three minutes to go in the game.

videos.headline: Landers' 3 gives Dayton a late second-half lead

videos.description: Saint Louis' Jordan Goodwin scores a layup as time expires in the second half, sending the game to overtime.
